<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>extravagant in something • extravagant with something</xh5><p> <i>extravagant in something—</i>going beyond what is reasonable in smth. one does: Roger was a superb teacher of piano and his own students have frequently been <u>extravagant in</u> his praise.</p><p><i>extravagant with something—</i>going beyond what is reasonable in smth. one uses or spends: While unbelievably good-looking and <u>extravagant with</u> his money, his accent takes away from his affluent upbringing.</p> </entry>
